window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>World-class crime writer Val McDermid has sold millions of copies of her books worldwide. In <i>The Retribution,</i> clinical psychologist Tony Hill and detective Carol Jordan face a terrifying reality: Serial killer Jacko Vance has escaped imprisonment - and appears hell-bent on revenge against those who put him behind bars.</p>"; 
